{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 77,
  "title": "第七十七章（天道）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天之道，其猶張弓與！"
    },
    {
      "text": "高者抑之，下者舉之，有餘者損之，不足者補之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天之道，損有餘而補不足。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之道則不然，損不足以奉有餘。"
    },
    {
      "text": "孰能有餘以奉天下？唯有道者。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人為而不恃，"
    },
    {
      "text": "功成而不處，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其不欲見賢。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天道暗昧，舉物類以為喻也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言張弓和調之，如是乃可用耳，夫抑高舉下，損強益弱，天之道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天道損有餘而益謙，常以中和為上。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人道則與天道反，世俗之人損貧以奉富，奪弱以益強也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言誰能居有餘之位，自省爵祿以奉天下不足者乎？唯有道之君能行也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人為德施，不恃其報也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "功成事就，不處其位。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不欲使人知己之賢，匿功不居榮，畏天損有餘也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
